Class ImgCropLayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.lang.NNLayer

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LayerPrecision<ImgCropLayer>, Serializable

    public class ImgCropLayer
extends NNLayer
implements LayerPrecision<ImgCropLayer>
    Reduces the resolution of the input by selecting a centered window. The output image will have the same number of color bands.
